des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : shechunhao@ahjiahong.com
Amazon Alexa and the Smart thermostats work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the thermostat. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home thermostat - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your smart thermostat in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our 'Warmme' app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Smart account in our 'Warmme' app;
(3). You need to have some Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our 'Warmme' app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Warmme" skills;
(5). Download Amazon 'Alexa' app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with 'Alexa' app;
(7). Search 'Warmme' skill from the 'Alexa' app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of 'Warmme', and you'll be navigated to Warmme login page;
(9). Input your account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“What's thermostat set to?"
“Alexa, Set the thermostat to 20 degrees."
“Alexa, turn on thermostat."

Currently this skill supports products:
smart switch,
smart socket, 
smart bulb....
